                <br>
                <p>I don't like to define myself by the work I have done. I define myself by the work towards the goals I am headed. Skills can be taught, personality is inherent. I prefer to keep learning, continue challenging myself, and do interesting things that are both aligned and not aligned to my future goals.</p>
